OL,3,CMan who dumped black sack of rubbish
OL,4,Cin layby fined #1000 for fly-tipping
OL,6,FA man from Berkshire who dumped one
OL,7,Fblack sack of household waste in a
OL,8,Flayby in a Buckinghamshire village has
OL,9,Fbecome the first person in the county
OL,10,Fto be fined #1000 for fly-tipping.
OL,12,FThe man from Bracknell, stopped in the
OL,13,Flayby in Denham and dumped the sack on
OL,14,Fthe A412 on 20 December 2023, just two
OL,15,Fdays after Buckinghamshire Council
OL,16,Fagreed the new higher penalty rate.
OL,18,FHe waited until he thought the coast
OL,19,Fwas clear and then dumped the sack at
OL,20,Fthe roadside behind the car he was
OL,21,Fdriving.
