OL,6,FBut he was caught on a traffic
OL,7,Fmonitoring camera, and when he was
OL,8,Finterviewed, he claimed he'd been
OL,9,Ffeeling unwell and the smell from the
OL,10,Fsack was overpowering.
OL,12,FThe council revealed the rubbish in
OL,13,Fthe sack - mainly drinks containers
OL,14,Fand wrappers, could have been freely
OL,15,Frecycled either at home or at a
OL,16,Fcouncil recycling centre.
