OL,6,FThomas Broom, Buckinghamshire
OL,7,FCouncil's Cabinet Member for Climate
OL,8,FChange and Environment said:
OL,9,F"Buckinghamshire Council is determined
OL,10,Fto demonstrate its Zero Tolerance of
OL,11,Ffly-tipping, whether it be commercial
OL,12,Fcriminal dumping or the kind of low-
OL,13,Flevel stupidity we see in a case like
OL,14,Fthis; we want to send a clear message
OL,15,Fto people that it will not be
OL,16,Ftolerated, and we will pursue you.
