OL,6,F"For these lower-level cases, the
OL,7,Foffender's admission means we can now
OL,8,Fdeal with it at the fixed penalty
OL,9,Flevel rather than prosecuting the case
OL,10,Fat court, meaning our officers are
OL,11,Fable to focus their efforts on more
OL,12,Fprolific offending.
OL,14,F"The culprit has paid the #1,000 and
OL,15,Favoided court but is out of pocket by
OL,16,Fa large amount of money and will
OL,17,Fhopefully think twice about doing
OL,18,Fsomething like this again.
