OL,6,F"The laybys on the A412 are regularly
OL,7,Fsubjected to fly-tipping and the
OL,8,Fditches can become clogged with dumped
OL,9,Fwaste. These ditches are meant to
OL,10,Fallow surface water drainage to
OL,11,Fmaintain a safe surface for road users
OL,12,Fand should not be viewed as a dumping
OL,13,Fground.
OL,15,F"The required traffic control measures
OL,16,Fto allow safe removal of dumped waste
OL,17,Ffrom fast roads presents council tax-
OL,18,Fpayers with a bill of tens of
OL,19,Fthousands of pounds annually."
